					<div class="state_content">
						<h4><span class="state_username">琴琴</span>&nbsp;赞了TA的文章&nbsp;《<span class="state_username">标题/此为标题</span>》</h4>
						<p class="state_updatetime">2016-08-24 15:33:23</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="state state_comment">
					<div class="state_userhead">
						<img src="/img/share.png">
					</div>
					<div class="state_content">
						<h4><span class="state_username">琴琴</span>&nbsp;评论了TA的文章&nbsp;《<span class="state_username">标题/此为标题</span>》</h4>
						<p class="state_updatetime">2016-08-24 15:33:23</p>
						<p class="state_comment_content">受益匪浅，赞赞赞~</p>
